# Identity (ADI)

## Setup

```go
liteKey := GenerateKey()
liteAddr := LiteAddress(liteKey, ACME)
Faucet(liteAddr).
	Wait()
Transaction(liteAddr).
	WithSigner(liteAddr).
	AddCredits(liteAddr, 100).
		Oracle(5).
	Initiate(liteKey).
	Submit().
	Wait()
```
## Create an ADI

```go{ id: 1 }
aliceKey := GenerateKey("alice")
Show(Transaction(liteAddr).
	WithSigner(liteAddr).
	CreateIdentity("alice").
		WithKey(aliceKey).
		WithKeyBook("alice/book").
	Initiate(liteKey).
	Submit().
	Wait())
Show(Get("alice"))
```

