## Add credits to the key page

```go{ id: 2 }
Transaction(liteAddr).
	WithSigner(liteAddr).
	AddCredits("alice/book/1", 100).
		Oracle(5).
	Initiate(liteKey).
	Submit().
	Wait()
Show(Get("alice/book/1"))
```

